%% Diagram: Crypto-shredding for GDPR right-to-erasure
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Command handler
    participant Keys as Key store (mutable)
    participant ES as Event store (append-only)
    participant Proj as Projection
    Note over App,Proj: Write path
    App->>Keys: getOrCreateKey(subjectId)
    Keys-->>App: subjectKey
    App->>App: encrypt PII with subjectKey to ciphertext
    App->>ES: append(event with ciphertext, subjectId)
    Note over App,Proj: Erasure (right-to-be-forgotten)
    App->>Keys: deleteKey(subjectId)
    Keys-->>App: ok
    Note over ES: Events untouched, ciphertext now unreadable
    Note over App,Proj: Read after erasure
    Proj->>ES: readStream(subjectId)
    ES-->>Proj: events with ciphertext
    Proj->>Keys: getKey(subjectId)
    Keys-->>Proj: null
    Proj->>Proj: render tombstone ([deleted])
    Proj-->>App: read model with tombstones
